parts.text:
```json
{
  "application": "Stable Diffusion",
  "software_requirements": [
    "intelmpi",
    "CUDA 11.0",
    "NCCL",
    "AWS OFI NCCL",
    "Amazon EFA",
    "Python",
    "MPI"
  ],
  "resource_requirements": {
    "partition": "compute-od-gpu",
    "nodes": 32,
    "tasks_per_node": 1,
    "cpus_per_gpu": 4,
    "gpus": 8,
    "exclusive": true,
    "output": "%x_%j.out",
    "comment": "Key=Monitoring,Value=ON",
    "no_requeue": true
  },
  "environment_variables": [
    "LD_LIBRARY_PATH",
    "NCCL_PROTO",
    "PATH",
    "LD_PRELOAD",
    "FI_EFA_FORK_SAFE",
    "FI_LOG_LEVEL",
    "FI_EFA_USE_DEVICE_RDMA",
    "NCCL_DEBUG",
    "PYTHONFAULTHANDLER",
    "CUDA_LAUNCH_BLOCKING",
    "OMPI_MCA_mtl_base_verbose",
    "FI_EFA_ENABLE_SHM_TRANSFER",
    "FI_PROVIDER",
    "FI_EFA_TX_MIN_CREDITS",
    "NCCL_TREE_THRESHOLD",
    "HOSTNAMES",
    "MASTER_ADDR",
    "MASTER_PORT",
    "COUNT_NODE",
    "WORLD_SIZE"
  ]
}
```
